&lt;p&gt;GitHub：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL21lbmdrdW5zb2Z0L01LT25saW5lTXVzaWNQbGF5ZXI=&#34;&gt;https://github.com/mengkunsoft/MKOnlineMusicPlayer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2020/05/10/oW7pxCytvQaTNHf.png&#34; alt=&#34;播放列表&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
